author: Jorge C.
title: Jorge C.
text: I've order products from Thread Logic on many occasions and each time I've been very pleased with the quality of service, professionalism, and product I experienced. They deliver a quality product on time, they communicate clearly during the project providing clear guidelines on expectations and timing, and offer competitive pricing. I'm very pleased with Thread Logic and would certainly recommend them to anyone.
